		{
			"type": "action",
			"name": "Leave This Tomb",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "action"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The grave protector has a creature @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.kWc1fhmv9LBiTuei]{Grabbed}.</p><hr /><p> The grave protector toss away the creature it grabbed up to 20 feet in any direction away from the grave protector and its grave. The affected creature takes @Damage[4d6[bludgeoning]] damage (@Check[fortitude|dc:22|basic|options:damaging-effect] save), falling @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.j91X7x0XSomq8d60]{Prone} on a failure or critical failure. If the target creature would end in the space of another creature, the target creature ends in a free- space within 5 feet of the second creature and both will take the bludgeoning damage with the basic save. The second creature would consider the result as one degree better.</p><p></p>",
